data_table.name: MESA_AirNRAorticCalciumCT
data_table.description: MESA Air New Recruit Aortic CT Ancillary Dataset: The MESA Aortic CT Exam is an ancillary exam of the MESA Study. This dataset consists of aortic CT phenotype variables including, but not limited to measurements of coronary calcium quantity by Agatston score, calcium volume and mass for MESA Air New Recruits at thier baseline exam.
